fields.description: Do it All, and Do it Faster: As modern CPUs feature more and more cores, the unprecedented speed of DDR5 ensures your high-end CPU gets data quickly, enabling faster processing, rendering, and buffering than ever before. Compact Form-Factor: Low clearance ensures wide compatibility with nearly any DDR5 build.

fields.name: Corsair Vengeance RGB RT 32GB (2x16GB) DDR4 4000MHz
fields.description:
Dynamic RGB Lighting: Illuminate your system with dynamic ten-zone RGB lighting with individually addressable RGB LEDs encased in a panoramic light pipe that offers viewing from virtually every angle. Create and Customise: Choose from dozens of preset lighting profiles, or create your own in CORSAIR iCUE software. Optimised for AMD Motherboards: Achieve top bandwidth and tight response times on the latest AMD DDR4 motherboards to complement your cutting-edge Ryzen system.

Dual-Tone Aluminum Heatspreader: Conducts heat away from your memory for superb cooling even when overclocked, with distinctive dual-tone styling to complement your system build. Maximum Speed Boost: Automatically configures to maximum supported speed on compatible systems for faster load times, multitasking, and more right out of the box – no need to set in BIOS. Custom Performance PCB: Provides the highest signal quality for the greatest level of performance and stability.

Powered by 3rd generation AMD Ryzen 9, Ryzen7, Ryzen 5 AM4 to maximize connectivity and speed with dual M.2, PCIe 4.0, USB 3.2 Gen2 and up to 128 GB of DDR4 (4400 MHz). With 3rd Gen Ryzen processors, this motherboard features the recent Lightning Gen 4 solution on both PCI-E and M.2 slot, which allow for faster data transfer on graphics cards, storage devices and networking devices. AUDIO BOOST which rewards your ears with studio grade sound quality for more immersive gaming experience.
